==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One acre, three parts of a piece of land.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī mŭ sān fēn dì

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[亩]][[三]][[分]][[地]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# A tiny piece of land.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[畝]][[三]][[分]][[地]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

